## Testing New Action

```ruby
test "should get new" do
  sign_in_as @user
  get new_article_url
  
  assert_response :success
  assert_not_nil assigns(:article)
end

test "redirects to login if not authenticated" do
  get new_article_url
  
  assert_redirected_to login_url
end
```

